com.facebook.litho

Interface ComponentLifecycle.RenderData

  • Enclosing class:
    ComponentLifecycle

    public static interface ComponentLifecycle.RenderData
    A per-Component-class data structure to keep track of some of the last mounted @Prop/@State params a component was rendered with. The exact params that are tracked are just the ones needed to support that Component's use of Diff params in their lifecycle methods that allow Diff params (e.g. ComponentLifecycle.onCreateTransition(com.facebook.litho.ComponentContext)).
